HEADWORD: Revivificate
<hw>Re`vi*vif"i*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>vivificate</ets>: cf. L. <ets>revivificare</ets>,
<ets>revivificatum</ets>. Cf. <er>Revivify</er>.]</ety> <def>To revive;
to recall or restore to life.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
